  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc7\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bb5 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd ; \u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0baf \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Can help Sri Lanka in line with policies; International Monetary Fund Report",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The visiting IMF delegation has informed President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa that they look forward to assisting Sri Lanka in this dire situation in line with their policies.",
        "The International Monetary Fund (IMF) delegation, which visited the country on Monday the 20th, is staying here until the 30th to explore ways to help resolve the economic crisis. The group held its first meeting with Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe on the day of his visit to the country. However, the Prime Minister's Office said it would not release information on the issues discussed during the meeting.",
        "In this context, the Committee met with President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa at the Presidential Palace on Friday. During the meeting, it was pointed out that they could assist Sri Lanka in pursuing their policies.",
        "The IMF delegation, which is staying in the country for a week, is conducting a detailed study on reaching an executive working group level agreement and on policy issues.",
        "The delegation briefed Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe, the Finance Ministry, the Governor of the Central Bank and other economic officials, discussions with experts and briefed President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa on the current situation.",
        "Elaborating on the current economic situation, the President thanked the delegation for assisting Sri Lanka in this difficult situation.",
        "Peter Brewer, Senior Executive Chairman of the International Monetary Fund; Amarasekara, Central Bank Governor Dr. Nandalal Weerasinghe, Finance Ministry Secretary K.M. Siriwardena, Deputy Finance Secretary M.S.S. Saman Fernando, Deputy Governor DMJYP Fernando and Director of the Department of Economic Research Dr. PKG. It is noteworthy that Harischandra also attended the meeting."
      ],
